name: Cal.com Trigger
natural_language_description: 这是 Cal.com Trigger 节点。主要用于: Handle Cal.com events via webhooks

events.name: events
events.natural_language_description: 参数名: Events | 默认值: [] | (必填项)
available_options: Booking Cancelled (值: BOOKING_CANCELLED) - Receive notifications when a Cal event is canceled
Booking Created (值: BOOKING_CREATED) - Receive notifications when a new Cal event is created
Booking Rescheduled (值: BOOKING_RESCHEDULED) - Receive notifications when a Cal event is rescheduled
Meeting Ended (值: MEETING_ENDED) - Receive notifications when a Cal event or meeting has ended

version.name: version
version.natural_language_description: 参数名: API Version | 默认值: 2

options.name: options
options.natural_language_description: 参数名: Options | 默认值: {}
available_options: appId (值: None) - The ID of the App to monitor
eventTypeId (值: None) - The EventType to monitor. Choose from the list, or specify an ID using an expression.
payloadTemplate (值: None) - Template to customize the webhook payload
